race.comment: SUMMIT (9) progressed nicely last start when he made late ground to finish a close second over 1100m at Ipswich after missing the placings at the previous appearance. Nicely placed to play a pivotal role. CHAMPAGNE SUNSET (19) debuted three weeks ago when he finished fifth over 1200m at Gold Coast, beaten 2.25 lengths. Fitter now and with the blinkers added is sure to be competitive. MEDIA BRIEF (14) will strip fitter second up and the extra 100m should be in her favour. PENSIERO (11) showed improvement to place last time out and should be at peak fitness now.
